data.description: Welcome to 1667 Constant Trail in the Luz Del Sol community built by Signature homes. This single story home is located on the corner of a cul-d-sac with 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an office and a 3 car garage. The front yard has water efficient landscaping leading up to a covered entry porch. Enter through the front door to the open floor plan great room with 9’ ceilings, dining room area, spacious living room and large kitchen. The kitchen features an island with bar seating, granite countertops with full backsplash, Energy Star black/stainless range/oven, microwave, dishwasher, solid wood/raised panel white cabinets w/soft close drawer guides and door hinges, stainless steel under mount sink, high efficiency recessed lights and mason jar lights over the island. The office is located to the right of the front entry, perfectly placed to see any visitors walking up the driveway. The spacious master bedroom has a large walk in closet and an attached ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, separate shower and soaking tub. Down the hall you will find the remaining 3 bedrooms, a full bathroom, the laundry room and a guest bathroom. This Signature home also features tile throughout, energy efficient dual glazed low-E vinyl tempered windows w/blinds throughout, tankless water heater, interior fire sprinkler system and hardwired smoke /carbon monoxide detectors. Spacious backyard with a generous concrete patio, lush grass and vinyl/block fencing, providing comfort and privacy. Close proximity to the Ramona Expressway for commuting and minutes to local shopping, restaurants and schools. This no HOA and lower tax home is a must see.
